<eesti>&sect; 37. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 37. </inglise>
<eesti>T&ouml;&ouml;tajale ekslikult v&auml;ljamakstud summade tagasin&otilde;udmine </eesti>
<inglise>Reclamation of amounts erroneously paid to employee </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kui t&ouml;&ouml;andja on t&ouml;&ouml;tajale arvutusvea t&otilde;ttu maksnud palka v&otilde;i h&uuml;vitust etten&auml;htust rohkem, on tal &otilde;igus rohkem makstud summad t&ouml;&ouml;tajalt kinni pidada kolme kuu jooksul, arvates nende maksmise v&otilde;i t&ouml;&ouml;taja pangakontole &uuml;lekandmise p&auml;evast, kui t&ouml;&ouml;taja ei vaidle nende kinnipidamise aluse v&otilde;i suuruse vastu. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) If, due to a calculation error, an employer pays an employee more wages or compensation than prescribed, the employer has the right to deduct such amounts within three months from the date of payment or transfer to the employee's bank account, unless the employee disputes the basis or amount of the deduction. </inglise>
<eesti>(16.05.2001 j&otilde;ust.11.06.2001 - RT I 2001, 50, 287) </eesti>
<inglise>(16.05.2001 entered into force 11.06.2001 - RT I 2001, 50, 287) </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Muudel p&otilde;hjustel t&ouml;&ouml;tajale ekslikult makstud v&otilde;i tema pangakontole &uuml;lekantud summad tagasin&otilde;udmisele ei kuulu, v&auml;lja arvatud juhul, kui maksmise aluseks olid t&ouml;&ouml;taja poolt teadvalt esitatud valeandmed v&otilde;i v&otilde;ltsitud dokumendid. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Amounts otherwise paid to an employee or transferred to an employee's bank account erroneously are not subject to reclamation, except in the case where payment was based on false information or forged documents knowingly presented by the employee. </inglise>
<eesti>(16.05.2001 j&otilde;ust.11.06.2001 - RT I 2001, 50, 287) </eesti>
<inglise>(16.05.2001 entered into force 11.06.2001 - RT I 2001, 50, 287) </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Teadvalt esitatud valeandmete v&otilde;i v&otilde;ltsitud dokumentide alusel liigselt makstud summasid on t&ouml;&ouml;andjal &otilde;igus tagasi n&otilde;uda seaduses etten&auml;htud aja jooksul. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) An employer has the right to reclaim excessive amounts paid to an employee on the basis of knowingly presented false information or forged documents during the period prescribed by law. </inglise>
