<eesti>Vabariigi Valitsusel on &otilde;igus anda m&auml;&auml;rusi k&auml;esoleva seaduse alusel ja t&auml;itmiseks. </eesti>
<inglise>The Government of the Republic has the right to issue regulations on the basis and for the implementation of this Act. </inglise>
